OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHeat pump grants worth     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F#5,000 to help replace gas 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fboilers                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Homeowners in England and Wales will be
OL,6, offered subsidies of #5,000 from next  
OL,7, April to help them to replace old gas  
OL,8, boilers with low-carbon heat pumps.    
OL,10,FUp to 25 million UK homes are heated by
OL,11,Fgas boilers, but the grants will fund  
OL,12,Fjust 90,000 pumps over three years.    
OL,14,FThe government says it wants no new gas
OL,15,Fboilers to be sold after 2035, but has 
OL,16,Fnot yet banned them altogether.        
OL,18,FExperts have criticised the plans as   
OL,19,Funambitious, but the government says it
OL,20,Fwill boost demand for heat pumps.      
